item.title: CVE-2018-5203|2024-08-05T05:26:47.205Z -- devpia -- dextuploadx5
item.description: DEXTUploadX5 version Between 1.0.0.0 and 2.2.0.0 contains a vulnerability that could allow remote attacker to download and execute remote arbitrary file by setting the arguments to the activex method. this can be leveraged for code execution.
